Package: gammarus.phosphorum
Title: Population-level Tests of the Growth Rate Hypothesis in Gammarus
    fossarum
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Titouan", 
        family = "Dionet",
        role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        email = "titouan.dionet@univ-lorraine.fr",
        comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-5602-1873")))
Description: Companion code to Dionet et al. (in prep.) testing the Growth
    Rate Hypothesis at the population level in Gammarus fossarum. Provides
    functions for size-structured matrix population modeling, stoichiometric
    calculations, and simulation tools to explore the relationship between
    population growth rate and phosphorus content. Raw data are archived
    separately [DOI to be completed]. The manuscript is available as a preprint
    [DOI to be completed].
